					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thanks for the crit. I've edited the log a bit &#8212; they start procrastinating it more and more before eventually deciding to hang onto it. Also re-arranged one of the logs to make it more clear how the social thing is working, at that point it's on auto so it feeds it directly to them without needing to have it in front of them to type in or directly see.</p> 
