					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12856253#post-4447880</guid>
				<title>Site Criticism Team - Staff Review</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12856253/scp-4527#post-4447880</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2019 14:46:07 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>TheMightyMcB</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4483018</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This one just barely eeks out the upvote from me, I think. My main issue was the logs. The researcher doesn't feel like they're reacting like a normal person would. Their decision to keep the phone at first just feels rushed, like they had no real internal debate on it at all. &quot;I'll do it tomorrow&quot; turned into &quot;I'll just hold onto it&quot; out of nowhere.</p> <p>Additionally, little details stuck out to me as odd. Like, how did this guy use it to navigate social situations? Was he just staring at his phone in conversations with his boss? Almost reminds me of that recent episode of Rick and Morty with the crystals that show you how you die.</p> <p>The awkwardness in the log wasn't enough to detract from my upvote, but it was close.</p> <p><span style="font-size:smaller;"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> <em>Opinions expressed in this review do not reflect the opinions of SCP Wiki staff as a whole. Please respond to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576517710" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span> or contact the captain of the Site Criticism Team, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576517710" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span>, for any questions or concerns relating to this review.</em></span></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
