				<wikidot:authorName>Simartar</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5489226</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>After about a month of sitting on it, finally up. Thank you everyone who critted this:</p> <p><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5549954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="Dyslexion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5549954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dyslexion" >Dyslexion</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tupacofficial" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3101862&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="tupacofficial" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3101862)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tupacofficial" >tupacofficial</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5717239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="Kybard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5717239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kybard" >Kybard</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5045819&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="Calibri Bold" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5045819)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/calibri-bold" >Calibri Bold</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4646198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="BlueJones" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4646198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" >BlueJones</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5379342&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="redredred" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5379342)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/redredred" >redredred</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wmaitla" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5048887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="wmaitla" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5048887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wmaitla" >wmaitla</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5588260&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="JakdragonX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5588260)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakdragonx" >JakdragonX</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1989312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="Doctor Fullham" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1989312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" >Doctor Fullham</a></span><br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thehouseofballoons" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3369416&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1576646983" alt="TheHouseOfBalloons" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3369416)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/thehouseofballoons" >TheHouseOfBalloons</a></span><br /> &#8230;and more &#8212; if I forgot, feel free to tell me and I'll edit you in.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;close</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Parts of the skip's narrative ended up as little hints and implications, which is hilarious in hindsight since I pretty much need to be whacked over the head by a baseball bat shaped like the story to get an article.</p> <p>Essentially, the little strike-out at the end is meant to imply that it's affecting a new person now - Katherine Tindall, and it's using that to make itself Thaumiel. I personally headcanon that the app's previous actions were trying to push Zhou up the Foundation by encouraging them to take the promotion, but when they stopped being cooperative it made them out to be crazy so it could be reassigned to a new researcher &#8212; but that's all up to interpretation, I suppose. A lot of the stuff here I tried to keep kind of murky.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Anyways, thanks for reading!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
